1. Executive Summary
Product Name

BizDaily

Tagline

Know Your Numbers. Grow Your Business.

Overview

BizDaily is an AI-powered mobile application that helps Small and Medium-sized Enterprises (SMEs) understand their business performance through simple daily business reporting.

Unlike traditional accounting software, POS systems, or bookkeeping applications, BizDaily does not require users to record every sale or expense individually.

Instead, at the end of each business day, users spend less than one minute entering:

Total Sales
Total Expenses

If customers purchased on credit, users can optionally record those debts.

BizDaily automatically:

Calculates daily profit.
Tracks outstanding customer debts.
Generates business performance insights.
Calculates a Business Score.
Produces weekly and monthly reports.
Highlights trends that help business owners make informed decisions.

The application is designed with a mobile-first approach, recognizing that many African SMEs primarily use smartphones to manage their businesses.

2. Vision

To become Africa's simplest and most trusted AI-powered business intelligence platform for small businesses.

3. Mission

To help every small business owner understand the health of their business by transforming simple daily reports into meaningful insights and smarter business decisions.

4. Problem Statement

Millions of small business owners across Africa do not keep consistent business records.

Existing accounting applications are often:

Too complicated
Too expensive
Require bookkeeping knowledge
Require recording every transaction
Designed for accountants instead of entrepreneurs

As a result, many business owners cannot answer simple questions such as:

Am I making profit?
Are my expenses increasing?
Who still owes me money?
Is my business improving?
How did I perform last month?

BizDaily solves this problem by reducing business reporting to less than one minute per day.

5. Goals

The MVP aims to:

Make daily business reporting simple.
Encourage consistent reporting.
Provide instant business insights.
Help users monitor debts.
Generate professional reports.
Demonstrate AI-assisted business intelligence.
6. Success Metrics

The MVP will be considered successful if users can:

✅ Record today's business in under one minute.

✅ View their latest business report immediately.

✅ Track customer debts.

✅ Generate weekly reports.

✅ Generate monthly reports.

✅ Export reports as PDF or Excel.

✅ Understand their business through AI insights.

