10. Core Product Principles

The product must always remain:

Simple

Users should spend less than one minute recording their business.

Intelligent

The application should explain numbers instead of merely displaying them.

Mobile First

The primary experience is smartphones.

Desktop exists only as a responsive version.

Automatic

Users should never enter:

Date
Day
Profit
Business Score

The system calculates these automatically.

Honest Reporting

If a user misses a day, the application should never estimate values.

Instead, display:

No Business Report Submitted

Sales

Nil

Expenses

Nil

Profit

Nil

This ensures weekly and monthly reports remain accurate.

